<paragraph pageId="14" pageNumber="83">
Other original material includes: Iran, Prov. Aderbeidschan. distr. Khoi, ad Seidchadzi, 18 May 1828, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="83">Szovits 258</emphasis>
(LE!, LE0009678 [image!], LE0009679, LE0009680 [image!], LE0009681 [image!], W0028250 [image!]; In apricis prov. Aderbeidschan e Karabahg, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="83">Fischer</emphasis>
[herb. Fischer] (K000789867 [image!]). 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Poa" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Poa persica" order="Poales" pageId="14" pageNumber="83" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="persica">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="83">Poa persica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has two major variations: subsp. 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Poa" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Poales" pageId="14" pageNumber="83" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" subspecies="persica">persica</taxonomicName>
