<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Poa" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Poales" pageId="14" pageNumber="83" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" subspecies="multiflora">multiflora</taxonomicName>
with glabrous lemmas and relatively greater panicle length to plant height ratio, and often more flowers per spikelet.
</paragraph>
